==Profit analysis==
Based on the percentages above, you can discern the approximate amount of profit you will make per box. Because prices are constantly fluctuating, the profit can vary, but it is highly unlikely that you will lose profit when buying herb boxes.

The estimated profit per box based off the percentages in the table is {{NoCoins|{{#vardefineecho:boxprofit|{{#expr:10 * ({{GEP|Grimy guam leaf|32/128}} + {{GEP|Grimy marrentill|24/128}} + {{GEP|Grimy tarromin|18/128}} + {{GEP|Grimy harralander|14/128}} + {{GEP|Grimy ranarr weed|11/128}} + {{GEP|Grimy irit leaf|8/128}} + {{GEP|Grimy avantoe|6/128}} + {{GEP|Grimy kwuarm|5/128}} + {{GEP|Grimy cadantine|4/128}} + {{GEP|Grimy lantadyme|3/128}} + {{GEP|Grimy dwarf weed|3/128}})}}}}|c}}, for a value of {{NoCoins|{{#var:boxprofit}} / 9500|c}} per Nightmare Zone point.

Assuming that you open the highest number of herb boxes possible per day (which is 15) for 142,500 Nightmare Zone points, you may get a total average profit of {{NoCoins|15 *{{#var:boxprofit}}|c}}.

